{"translationLines":[{"lineNumber":217372,"originalJapaneseLine":"あなたは長田君と一緒に","translatedEnglishLine":"You were together with Nagata-kun,"},{"lineNumber":217373,"originalJapaneseLine":"二人の手慣れた作業を観察していた。","translatedEnglishLine":"observing the two skillfully performing their task."},{"lineNumber":217374,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},

{"lineNumber":217375,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ん？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm?\""},

{"lineNumber":217376,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……んだよ？　何見てんだよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...What? What are you looking at?\""},

{"lineNumber":217377,"originalJapaneseLine":"「いや、ちょっ！？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"No, wait!?\""},

{"lineNumber":217378,"originalJapaneseLine":"　先に見てたのそっちじゃねえか！」","translatedEnglishLine":"You were the one who was watching first!\""},

{"lineNumber":217379,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ああ！？　見てねーよ！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh!? I'm not looking!\""},

{"lineNumber":217380,"originalJapaneseLine":"　てめぇ、叩き割んぞ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'll smash you!\""},

{"lineNumber":217381,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ひいっ！　こわっ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Eek! Scary!\""},

{"lineNumber":217382,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あー、ごめんごめん。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, sorry, sorry."},

{"lineNumber":217383,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ザンスは裸にされる女の子モンスターに","translatedEnglishLine":"Zansu is just interested in the girl monsters being undressed,"},

{"lineNumber":217384,"originalJapaneseLine":"　興味あるだけだから許してあげて」","translatedEnglishLine":"so please forgive him.\" "},

{"lineNumber":217385,"originalJapaneseLine":"「へ？　そーなんすか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh? Really?\""},

{"lineNumber":217386,"originalJapaneseLine":"「むふっ♪」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Mufu♪\""},

{"lineNumber":217387,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おっとしっごろー♪」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oops, perfect timing♪\""},

{"lineNumber":217388,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なーんだ、そーなのかよ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh, is that so."},

{"lineNumber":217389,"originalJapaneseLine":"　それなら一緒に見ればいいのにー」","translatedEnglishLine":"If that's the case, you should watch together.\" "},

{"lineNumber":217390,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ば、馬鹿か！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"A-are you stupid!"},

{"lineNumber":217391,"originalJapaneseLine":"　今更女の子モンスターなんぞに興奮するか！」","translatedEnglishLine":"Do you think I'd get excited about girl monsters at this point?!\""},

{"lineNumber":217392,"originalJapaneseLine":"「えー、本当にー？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ehh, really?"},

{"lineNumber":217393,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ほらほら、この子とか可愛いよー？」","translatedEnglishLine":"Look, this one is cute, isn't she?\""},

{"lineNumber":217394,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はんッ！　俺を誰だと思ってる！","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmph! Who do you think I am!"},

{"lineNumber":217395,"originalJapaneseLine":"　リーザス国次代の国王である、","translatedEnglishLine":"I am Zansu Leesas, the next king of Leesas country,"},

{"lineNumber":217396,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ザンス・リーザスだぞ」","translatedEnglishLine":"Zansu Leesas.\" "},

{"lineNumber":217397,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それがなんなわけ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"So what about that?\""},

{"lineNumber":217398,"originalJapaneseLine":"「家庭の事情って奴だよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's because of family circumstances."},

{"lineNumber":217399,"originalJapaneseLine":"「俺にはガキの頃から","translatedEnglishLine":"Ever since I was a kid,"},

{"lineNumber":217400,"originalJapaneseLine":"　女が何人も用意されていたんだ」","translatedEnglishLine":"several women were prepared for me.\" "},

{"lineNumber":217401,"originalJapaneseLine":"「用意されていた！？","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Prepared for you!?"},

{"lineNumber":217402,"originalJapaneseLine":"　なにそれ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"What's that!?\""},

{"lineNumber":217403,"originalJapaneseLine":"「母さんの教育方針でな、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's my mother's educational policy,"},

{"lineNumber":217404,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いつか女を抱いた時に溺れすぎないよう","translatedEnglishLine":"to get me used to women from an early age, so I wouldn't become obsessed when I embraced one someday."},

{"lineNumber":217405,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ガキの内から慣れろってよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I was told to get used to it while still a kid.\" "},

{"lineNumber":217406,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ごくり……マジかよ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"*gulp*... Seriously...?\""},

{"lineNumber":217407,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おお！　マジだぞ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Yeah! It's true!\""},

{"lineNumber":217408,"originalJapaneseLine":"「人間の女に限っても百や二百は抱いたか……","translatedEnglishLine":"I've been with at least a hundred or two hundred human women..."},

{"lineNumber":217409,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いや、途中から数えてねーから","translatedEnglishLine":"Actually, I stopped counting somewhere along the way,"},

{"lineNumber":217410,"originalJapaneseLine":"　もう何人抱いてきたか覚えてないんだがな」","translatedEnglishLine":"so I don't even remember how many I've been with.\" "},

{"lineNumber":217411,"originalJapaneseLine":"「がはははははははは！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gahahahahahahaha!\""},

{"lineNumber":217412,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ままま、マジかよ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"R-really!?\""},

{"lineNumber":217413,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ハニ子は！？　ハニ子も抱いた！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What about Haniko!? Did you sleep with Haniko too!?\""},

{"lineNumber":217414,"originalJapaneseLine":"「……それは抱いてねーな」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"...I haven't slept with her.\" "},

{"lineNumber":217415,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そっか……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I see..."},

{"lineNumber":217416,"originalJapaneseLine":"　いや、しかしそれにしたって羨ましいな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"Well, even so, I'm jealous...\" "},

{"lineNumber":217417,"originalJapaneseLine":"「正直経験積みすぎて、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"To be honest, I've had so much experience,"},

{"lineNumber":217418,"originalJapaneseLine":"　今じゃろくな女じゃやる気もしねーくらいよ！」","translatedEnglishLine":"that now I don't even get motivated by decent women!\""},

{"lineNumber":217419,"originalJapaneseLine":"「くーっ！　俺も同じこと言ってみてー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Damn! I want to say the same thing!\""},

{"lineNumber":217420,"originalJapaneseLine":"「がはははははははははははは！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gahahahahahahahahaha!\""},

{"lineNumber":217421,"originalJapaneseLine":"「くっそー……嫌な奴だけどよ……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Damn... he's an unpleasant guy, but..."},

{"lineNumber":217422,"originalJapaneseLine":"　正直に羨ましいぜぇ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"honestly, I'm jealous...\" "},

{"lineNumber":217423,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………。」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},

{"lineNumber":217424,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふふん、そーだろう。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmph, see?\" "},

{"lineNumber":217425,"originalJapaneseLine":"　俺様はすごいんだよ」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'm amazing."},

{"lineNumber":217426,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お前よりもな！」","translatedEnglishLine":"More than you!"},

{"lineNumber":217427,"originalJapaneseLine":"「がはははははははは！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Gahahahahahaha!\""},

{"lineNumber":217428,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ぬぐぐぐ……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ughhh..."},

{"lineNumber":217429,"originalJapaneseLine":"　嫌な奴だなぁ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"What an annoying guy...\" "},

{"lineNumber":217430,"originalJapaneseLine":"あなたはザンスに差をつけられていると感じた。","translatedEnglishLine":"You felt that Zansu was pulling ahead of you."},

{"lineNumber":217431,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ああ？　なんだぁ、お前照れてんのか？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh? What's this, are you embarrassed?\""}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなたは長田君と一緒に
二人の手慣れた作業を観察していた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: observing the two skillfully performing their task.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 先に見てたのそっちじゃねえか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You were the one who was watching first!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンスは裸にされる女の子モンスターに
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Zansu is just interested in the girl monsters being undressed,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 興味あるだけだから許してあげて」
それなら一緒に見ればいいのにー」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: If that's the case, you should watch together."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今更女の子モンスターなんぞに興奮するか！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Do you think I'd get excited about girl monsters at this point?!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ほらほら、この子とか可愛いよー？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Look, this one is cute, isn't she?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はんッ！　俺を誰だと思ってる！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmph! Who do you think I am!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス国次代の国王である、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I am Zansu Leesas, the next king of Leesas country,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ザンス・リーザスだぞ」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ever since I was a kid,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女が何人も用意されていたんだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: several women were prepared for me."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつか女を抱いた時に溺れすぎないよう
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: to get me used to women from an early age, so I wouldn't become obsessed when I embraced one someday.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ガキの内から慣れろってよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I was told to get used to it while still a kid."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「人間の女に限っても百や二百は抱いたか……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I've been with at least a hundred or two hundred human women...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、途中から数えてねーから
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Actually, I stopped counting somewhere along the way,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう何人抱いてきたか覚えてないんだがな」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so I don't even remember how many I've been with."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ハニ子は！？　ハニ子も抱いた！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What about Haniko!? Did you sleep with Haniko too!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いや、しかしそれにしたって羨ましいな……」

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "To be honest, I've had so much experience,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今じゃろくな女じゃやる気もしねーくらいよ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: that now I don't even get motivated by decent women!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「くーっ！　俺も同じこと言ってみてー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Damn! I want to say the same thing!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「がはははははははははははは！」
あなたはザンスに差をつけられていると感じた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You felt that Zansu was pulling ahead of you.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ああ？　なんだぁ、お前照れてんのか？」

translatedEnglishLine.description: The original line translated to English
